reviewText:
A really nice Bullet Hell game, it requires much concentration from the player to evade every single projectile, but on the low levels can be a good casual game.

+Its difficulties really increase since the lower difficulty (Easy) to the highest difficulty (Judgement), making him a balanced game, even for those who want a casual game and even for those who want a really challenger game.
+It has a unique style of graphic and level design, making use of the Cyberpunk Style and in futurists features too;
+Has 4 (four) types of airships, everyone of them having your unique mechanics and gameplay, making the player choose between one of them for better skills and having a better playthrough.

-It has a little number of stages;
-If you play for a long time in and high difficulty, it can make you eyeballs hurt a bit duo to the high level of bright particles;
-Could have a Airship Customization feature, so the player can make his own combos in his airship.
